data.text: List of Nobel Peace Prize winners from every year the award has been given out. All Nobel Peace Prize winners are listed below in order of popularity, but can be sorted by any column. People who won the Nobel Peace Prize award are listed along with photos for every Nobel Peace Prize winner that has a picture associated with their name online. You can click on the name of the Nobel Peace Prize award recipients to get more information about each. People who won the Nobel Peace Prize are usually listed by year, but on this list you've got a complete list of Nobel Peace Prize winners from all years. If this proves to not be a full list of Nobel Peace Prize winners, you can help make it so by adding to this one. This list includes the most memorable and well-known Nobel Peace Prize winners of all time. Anybody who won the Nobel Peace Prize usually has a picture associated with their name, so all the Nobel Peace Prize-winning people are listed here with photos when available. This list spans the history of the Nobel Peace Prize, so most of the famous Nobel Peace Prize winners are here and can be a good starting point for making a list of your favorites. This list answers the question "who are all the people who have ever won Nobel Peace Prize?" If you're looking for all the nominees, you can click the links above the title of this page to the Listopedia page where you'll find a directory of award nominees, as well as the rest of the award winners lists we have. You may want to copy this factual list to build your own just like it, re-rank it to fit your views, then publish it to share with your Facebook friends, Twitter followers or with any other social networks you're on. This is a list that includes items like International Labour Organization and Wangari Maathai. {#nodes}
